org.fest.swing.fixture
Class JTableFixture

java.lang.Object
  org.fest.swing.fixture.ComponentFixture<JTable>
      org.fest.swing.fixture.JTableFixture

public class JTableFixture
extends ComponentFixture<JTable>

Understands simulation of user events on a JTable and verification of the state of such JTable.

Author:
Alex Ruiz, Yvonne Wang, Fabien Barbero

doubleClick

public final JTableFixture doubleClick()
Simulates a user doble-clicking the JTable managed by this fixture.

Note: This method will not be successful if the double-clicking occurs on an editable table cell. For this particular case, this method will start edition of the table cell located under the mouse pointer.

Returns:
this fixture.
